item.title: Analyst skills
item.description: Analyst skills # I’m looking at the issue of analyst skills in the Nottinghamshire ICS with some other people at the moment. The brief is: This will quite obviously require a very large amount of information about analyst skills, careers, and training, and so I will be making notes as I go along here. There may be a couple of things that come out of this that I can’t share, thinking in particular of other people’s thoughts and ideas, but I’ll share as much as I can and hopefully this will prove a useful resource for somebody else doing the same thing in another part of the country (or world, even ðŸ˜‰)
